'''方慧蘭'''<ref name="明報131117">{{cite news |url=http://www.mingpaocanada.com/tor/htm/News/20131117/tgf1.htm?m=0 |title=方慧蘭競逐多市中心國會議席 |publisher=《[[明報|明報]]》加東版 |date=2013-11-17 |accessdate=2016-03-07 |archive-date=2017-03-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170318172553/http://www.mingpaocanada.com/tor/htm/News/20131117/tgf1.htm?m=0 |dead-url=no }}</ref> {{post-nominals|country=CAN|PC|MP}} （{{lang|en|Christina Alexandra "Chrystia" Freeland}}，{{bd|1968年|8月2日|||catIdx=Freeland, Chrystia}}），[[加拿大|加拿大]]{{Link-en|烏克蘭裔加拿大人|Ukrainian Canadians|烏克蘭裔}}政治人物、記者和作者，[[加拿大自由黨|加拿大自由黨]]黨員，2013年起擔任[[加拿大國會下議院|加拿大國會下議院]]議員，先後代表[[安大略省|安大略省]]的[[多倫多中選區|多倫多中選區]]和[[大學－玫瑰谷選區|大學－玫瑰谷選區]]，並於2015年自由黨上台執政後晉身[[賈斯汀·杜魯多内閣|賈斯汀·杜魯多内閣]]，先後出任聯邦國際貿易部長、外交部長、[[加拿大副總理|副總理]]兼跨政府事務部長和財政部長。從政前她為傳媒工作者，曾在《[[金融時報|金融時報]]》、《[[環球郵報|環球郵報]]》和[[湯森路透|湯森路透]]工作。

== 早年及個人生活 ==
方慧蘭生於[[亞伯達省|亞伯達省]][[皮斯里弗_(艾伯塔省)|和平河鎮]]<ref>[http://www.littlepinkbook.com/resources/pink-profiles/chrystia-freeland%20 littlepinkbook.com: interview with "Chrystia Freeland – U.S. Managing Editor, Financial Times" 20 May 2013] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130523004018/http://www.littlepinkbook.com/resources/pink-profiles/chrystia-freeland%20 |date=2013年5月23日 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ukrweekly.com/old/archive/2000/170011.shtml|title=Shevchenko Lecture focuses on Ukrainians and the media|author=Marco Levytsky|access-date=2016-03-08|archive-date=2013-09-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130928004931/http://www.ukrweekly.com/old/archive/2000/170011.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>，父親-{zh-cn:唐纳德; zh-hk:當奴; zh-tw:唐納德}-·弗里蘭（{{lang|en|}}Donald Freeland）為一名農夫和律師，持有[[加拿大自由黨|加拿大自由黨]]黨籍<ref name="canada.com">{{cite web|url=http://www.canada.com/edmontonjournal/news/cityplus/story.html?id=a706e023-9c09-4809-80d3-67a9d6ef2496&k=2780|title=Halyna Freeland's quest to 'change the world' influenced feminism in Alberta and Ukraine, and left a mark on her family and friends|website=Canada.com|date=July 14, 2007|accessdate=September 26, 2013|archive-date=2013-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131020224230/http://www.canada.com/edmontonjournal/news/cityplus/story.html?id=a706e023-9c09-4809-80d3-67a9d6ef2496&k=2780|dead-url=no}}</ref>；母親哈利娜（Halyna）亦為一名律師，並曾於1988年聯邦大選代表[[加拿大新民主黨|加拿大新民主黨]]在[[愛民頓|愛民頓]]競逐[[加拿大國會下議院|國會下議院]]議席<ref name=legacy>{{cite web|url=http://www.legacy.com/obituaries/edmontonjournal/obituary.aspx?pid=90579918#fbLoggedOut|title=Obituary: Halyna Chomiak Freeland|journal=Edmonton Journal|accessdate=September 26, 2013|archive-date=2013-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130927191101/http://www.legacy.com/obituaries/edmontonjournal/obituary.aspx?pid=90579918#fbLoggedOut|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="GM130727">{{cite news|url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/politics/journalist-chrystia-freeland-to-seek-liberal-nod-for-toronto-centre/article13470172/|title=Journalist Chrystia Freeland to seek Liberal nod for Toronto Centre|first=Daniel|last=LeBlanc|work=《[[環球郵報|環球郵報]]》|date=2013-07-27|accessdate=2016-03-07|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308171253/https://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/politics/journalist-chrystia-freeland-to-seek-liberal-nod-for-toronto-centre/article13470172/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。具烏克蘭血統的她能講英語、法語、俄羅斯語和烏克蘭語<ref>{{cite news|newspaper=《多倫多星報》|date=February 7, 2014|url=http://www.thestar.com/news/insight/2014/02/07/parliament_speaking_a_language_all_its_own.html|title=Parliament: Speaking a language all its own|accessdate=April 14, 2014|archive-date=2015-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151019065639/http://www.thestar.com/news/insight/2014/02/07/parliament_speaking_a_language_all_its_own.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="CBC140305">{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/government-to-send-military-observers-to-ukraine-1.2561288 |title=Government to send military observers to Ukraine |publisher=[[加拿大廣播公司|CBC News]] |date=2014-03-05 |accessdate=2016-03-06 |archive-date=2014-04-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140415064839/http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/government-to-send-military-observers-to-ukraine-1.2561288 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

方慧蘭於1986年從[[亞得里亞海聯合世界書院|亞得里亞海聯合世界書院]]畢業<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.uwc.org/alumni-bio/chrystia-freeland |title=Chrystia Freeland |work=United World Colleges |accessdate=2017-03-17 }}{{dead link|date=2018年3月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>，後到[[哈佛大學|哈佛大學]]主修俄羅斯歷史和文學。作為哈佛交流生，她到[[基輔|基輔]]深造烏克蘭語，並參與支持烏克蘭獨立。蘇聯黨媒批評她為「外部勢力」；[[KGB|KGB]]也嘗試監控她但不果，其機智與博學卻因而獲得當局暗中稱讚。<ref name=":3">{{Cite news|last=Miles|first=Simon|date=2021-10-11|title=KGB archives show how Chrystia Freeland drew the ire (and respect) of Soviet intelligence services|language=en-CA|work=The Globe and Mail|url=https://www.theglobeandmail.com/world/article-kgb-archives-show-how-chrystia-freeland-drew-the-ire-and-respect-of/|access-date=2021-10-13|archive-date=2021-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211126000256/https://www.theglobeandmail.com/world/article-kgb-archives-show-how-chrystia-freeland-drew-the-ire-and-respect-of/|dead-url=no}}</ref>在1989年被禁再踏足鐵幕下的烏克蘭後，方慧蘭於1990年取得文學士學位<ref>{{cite web |url=http://alumni.harvard.edu/events/your-harvard-new-york-city |title=Your Harvard: New York City |publisher=[[哈佛大學|哈佛大學]] |accessdate=2016-03-07 |archive-date=2020-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200412004923/https://alumni.harvard.edu/events/your-harvard-new-york-city |dead-url=no }}</ref>。後獲取[[羅德獎學金|羅德獎學金]]，在[[牛津大學聖安東尼學院|牛津大學聖安東尼學院]]深造，1993年取得研究碩士學位<ref name=ft>"Chrystia Freeland." [http://www.ft.com/cms/s/ae5c593e-ce42-11d7-81c6-0820abe49a01.html The Financial Times] biography. 3 Feb 2004; 26 May 2007.</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.oxfordtoday.ox.ac.uk/interviews/chrystia-freeland |title=Chrystia Freeland |work=Oxford Today |date=2011-03-22 |accessdate=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170118060751/http://www.oxfordtoday.ox.ac.uk/interviews/chrystia-freeland |archive-date=2017-01-18 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sant.ox.ac.uk/alumni-development/news/chrystia-freeland-appointed-canadian-minister-international-trade |title=Chrystia Freeland appointed Canadian Minister of International Trade |publisher=[[牛津大學聖安東尼學院|牛津大學聖安東尼學院]] |date=2015-11-11 |accessdate=2016-03-07 |archive-date=2020-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201017015337/https://www.sant.ox.ac.uk/alumni-development/news/chrystia-freeland-appointed-canadian-minister-international-trade |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

她的丈夫為《[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]》記者格拉厄姆·博利（{{lang|en|Graham Bowley}}）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nowaydownthebook.com/about-the-author/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2013-09-06 |date=2013-08-16 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130816225550/http://www.nowaydownthebook.com/about-the-author/ |archivedate=2013-08-16 }}</ref>，兩人育有三名子女<ref>{{cite news|url=http://o.canada.com/2013/07/29/chrystia-freeland-liberal-toronto-centre/|title=Chrystia Freeland to make U.S. Media Party care about Canadian politics|first=Marc|last=Weisblott|website=Canada.com|date=July 29, 2013|accessdate=September 6, 2013|archive-date=2013-08-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130823174935/http://o.canada.com/2013/07/29/chrystia-freeland-liberal-toronto-centre/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 記者和著作生涯 ==
[[File:Chrystia_Freeland_-_India_Economic_Summit_2011.jpg|thumb]]

方慧蘭在[[蘇聯解體|蘇聯解體]]後的[[烏克蘭|烏克蘭]]展開記者生涯，為《[[金融時報|金融時報]]》、《[[華盛頓郵報|華盛頓郵報]]》和《[[經濟學人|經濟學人]]》雜誌擔任特約記者<ref name="DFAIT bio">{{cite web |url=http://www.international.gc.ca/odskelton/freeland_bio.aspx?lang=eng&view=d |title=Chrystia Freeland |publisher=Foreign Affairs, International Trade and Development Canada |date=2015-12-09 |accessdate=2016-03-07 |archive-date=2013-07-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130720104547/http://www.international.gc.ca/odskelton/freeland_bio.aspx?lang=eng&view=d |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她後來正式加入《金融時報》，先後任職該報的副編輯、周末版編輯、網上版編輯、英國新聞編輯、莫斯科分局局長和東歐記者<ref name="DFAIT bio"/>。她於1999年轉任加拿大《[[環球郵報|環球郵報]]》副編輯，至2001年為止<ref name="DFAIT bio"/>，但其後仍繼續為該報撰寫專欄<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/report-on-business/chrystia-freelands-plutocrats-wins-national-business-book-award/article12212770/|location=Toronto|work=The Globe and Mail|title=Chrystia Freeland's Plutocrats wins National Business Book Award|date=May 28, 2013|accessdate=2016-03-08|archive-date=2021-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309055223/https://www.theglobeandmail.com/report-on-business/chrystia-freelands-plutocrats-wins-national-business-book-award/article12212770/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

她一度擔任《金融時報》的美國總編輯<ref name="Time130729">{{cite news |url=http://business.time.com/2013/07/29/prominent-journalist-chrystia-freeland-in-surprise-canadian-political-bid/ |title=Prominent Journalist Chrystia Freeland in Surprise Canadian Political Bid |publisher=《[[時代_(雜誌)|時代雜誌]]》 |first=Sam |last=Gustin |date=2013-07-29 |accessdate=2016-03-07 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305221802/http://business.time.com/2013/07/29/prominent-journalist-chrystia-freeland-in-surprise-canadian-political-bid/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，2010年則成為[[路透社|路透社]]的環球特約編輯（{{lang|en|global editor-at-large}}）<ref>{{cite press release |url=http://thomsonreuters.com/content/press_room/media/2010_03_01_chrystia_freeland |title=Chrystia Freeland Joins Reuters as Global Editor-at-large |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100304063037/http://thomsonreuters.com/content/press_room/media/2010_03_01_chrystia_freeland |archivedate=2010-03-04 |date=2010-03-01 |accessdate=2012-10-21 }}</ref>，2011年轉任[[湯森路透|湯森路透]]數碼編輯<ref>{{cite news|last=Saba|first=Jennifer|agency=Thomson Reuters|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/04/07/us-thomsonreuters-freeland-idUSTRE7366LB20110407|title=Chrystia Freeland named Thomson Reuters Digital editor|accessdate=December 6, 2012|date=April 7, 2011|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924152301/http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/04/07/us-thomsonreuters-freeland-idUSTRE7366LB20110407|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，後來改任該通訊社的常務經理和消費新聞編輯<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.thebaron.info/news/files/296a73d3b0d04b5b935ccb7e582e4d39-782.php|title='Journalistic excellence paramount' in the new Reuters|work=The Baron|date=December 19, 2012|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130919001250/http://www.thebaron.info/news/files/296a73d3b0d04b5b935ccb7e582e4d39-782.php|archivedate=2013年9月19日}}</ref>。

她於2000年出版的著作《世紀大拍賣：俄羅斯轉軌的内幕故事》（{{lang|en|''Sale of the Century''}}）講述俄羅斯在蘇聯解體後轉投資本主義的經過<ref name=ft/>；她後於2012年出版的《巨富：全球超級新貴的崛起及其他人的沒落》（{{lang|en|''Plutocrats: The Rise of the New Global Super-Rich and the Fall of Everyone Else''}}）登入[[紐約時報暢銷書榜|《紐約時報》暢銷書榜]]，並贏取2013年度{{le|萊昂內爾·格爾伯書獎|Lionel Gelber Prize}}<ref name="Time130729"/><ref>{{cite book|title=Plutocrats: the rise of the new global super-rich and the fall of everyone else|url=https://archive.org/details/plutocratsriseof0000chry|year=2012 |publisher=Penguin|location=New York|isbn=9781594204098|oclc=780480424}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/wonkblog/wp/2012/11/28/romney-is-wall-streets-worst-bet-since-the-bet-on-subprime/|title=Romney is Wall Street’s worst bet since the bet on subprime|work=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]]|author=Ezra Klein|date=November 28, 2012|accessdate=2016-03-08|archive-date=2015-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150722113925/http://www.washingtonpost.com/blogs/wonkblog/wp/2012/11/28/romney-is-wall-streets-worst-bet-since-the-bet-on-subprime/|dead-url=no}} Interview with Chrystia Freeland.</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/arts/books-and-media/plutocrats-author-chrystia-freeland-wins-15000-book-prize/article10300456/|location=Toronto|work=The Globe and Mail|title=Plutocrats author Chrystia Freeland wins $15,000 book prize for international affairs|date=March 25, 2013|accessdate=2016-03-08|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304211751/http://www.theglobeandmail.com/arts/books-and-media/plutocrats-author-chrystia-freeland-wins-15000-book-prize/article10300456/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 從政 ==
=== 初進國會 ===
[[賈斯汀·杜魯多|賈斯汀·杜魯多]]出任[[加拿大自由黨|加拿大自由黨]]黨魁後，不時在公開演講和媒體訪問時引述方慧蘭的書籍<ref name="Time130729"/>，而兩人亦有討論政策議題<ref name="GM130727"/>。兩人於2013年在渥太華某場合碰面時，杜魯多游說方慧蘭投身政界<ref name="GM130727"/>。隨著[[李博_(政治人物)|李博]]於2013年6月宣佈辭任[[多倫多中選區|多倫多中選區]]國會議員，方慧蘭於同年7月宣佈尋求該選區的自由黨候選人提名<ref name="GM130727"/><ref name="Time130729"/>。她於同年9月贏取自由黨候選人資格<ref name="Toronto Centre Byelection">{{cite news|url=http://news.nationalpost.com/2013/09/15/liberals-choose-chrystia-freeland-to-face-ndp-candidate-linda-mcquaig-in-upcoming-byelection-in-toronto-centre/|title=Liberals choose Chrystia Freeland to face NDP candidate Linda McQuaig in upcoming byelection in Toronto Centre|work=National Post|date=September 15, 2013|accessdate=September 15, 2013|author=Mok, Tanya}}</ref>，再於同年11月舉行的多倫多中選區議席補選中告捷，首度晉身[[加拿大國會下議院|國會下議院]]<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/politics/live-results-from-toronto-centre-and-three-other-federal-byelections/article15587457/|location=Toronto|work=The Globe and Mail|title=Complete results from Toronto Centre and three other federal by-elections|date=February 24, 2014|accessdate=November 26, 2013|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308130145/https://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/politics/live-results-from-toronto-centre-and-three-other-federal-byelections/article15587457/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她於2014年11月至2015年8月間擔任國會國際貿易常務委員會副主席<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.parl.gc.ca/Parliamentarians/en/members/Chrystia-Freeland(84665)/Roles | publisher=[[加拿大國會|加拿大國會]] | title=The Honourable Chrystia Freeland: All Roles | accessdate=2016-03-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170503084218/http://www.parl.gc.ca/Parliamentarians/en/members/Chrystia-Freeland(84665)/Roles | archive-date=2017-05-03 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

[[維克多·費奧多羅維奇·亞努科維奇|亞努科維奇]]於[[烏克蘭親歐盟示威運動|2014年2月辭任烏克蘭總統]]後，方慧蘭於同年3月代表自由黨到訪當地，期間與烏克蘭爭取改革民主同盟領袖[[維塔利·克利奇科|維塔利·克利奇科]]以及後於[[2014年烏克蘭總統選舉|同年5月當選總統]]的[[彼得·波羅申科|彼得·波羅申科]]等人會面<ref name="CBC140305"/>。加拿大政府於同年3月因[[2014年克里米亞危機|克里米亞併入俄羅斯聯邦]]而向俄國實施制裁和禁足令，俄羅斯政府遂於同月宣佈禁止包括方慧蘭在内的13名加拿大人入境<ref name="CBC140324">{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/russian-sanctions-against-canadians-a-badge-of-honour-1.2584137 |title=Russian sanctions against Canadians a 'badge of honour' |first=Susana |last=Mas |date=2014-03-24 |publisher=CBC News |accessdate=2016-03-08 |archive-date=2014-03-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140324205804/http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/russian-sanctions-against-canadians-a-badge-of-honour-1.2584137 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="明報140325">{{cite news |url=http://www.mingpaocanada.com/Tor/htm/News/20140325/tdd1.htm?m=0 |title=俄羅斯反擊 禁13加國政客入境 |publisher=《[[明報|明報]]》加東版 |date=2014-03-25 |accessdate=2016-03-08 |archive-date=2018-12-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181215065808/http://www.mingpaocanada.com/Tor/htm/News/20140325/tdd1.htm?m=0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>；方慧蘭在[[推特|推特]]發文表示這為一項榮譽<ref name="CBC140324"/>。

多倫多中選區在[[2015年加拿大國會下議院選舉|2015年聯邦大選]]重新劃分，方慧蘭改到新成立的[[大學－玫瑰谷選區|大學－玫瑰谷選區]]參選告捷<ref name="2015election">{{cite news|url=http://www.thestar.com/news/federal-election/federal-ridings-toronto-gta/2015/10/20/liberal-chrystia-freeland-wins-in-university-rosedale.html|title=Liberal Chrystia Freeland wins in University-Rosedale|newspaper=《多倫多星報》|date=October 20, 2015|accessdate=October 25, 2015|author=Otis, Daniel|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308153022/https://www.thestar.com/news/federal-election/federal-ridings-toronto-gta/2015/10/20/liberal-chrystia-freeland-wins-in-university-rosedale.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 內閣部長 ===
==== 國際貿易部長 ====
自由黨在2015年大選重拾執政權，方慧蘭於同年11月獲新任總理杜魯多委任為聯邦國際貿易部長，首度晉身[[加拿大內閣|內閣]]<ref name="CBC151104">{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/m/touch/politics/story/1.3304176 |title=Meet Justin Trudeau's new Liberal cabinet |publisher=[[加拿大廣播公司|CBC News]] |date=2015-11-04 |accessdate=2016-03-06 |archive-date=2017-03-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170319022208/http://www.cbc.ca/m/touch/politics/story/1.3304176 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她就職後延續上屆[[加拿大保守黨|保守黨政府]]與[[歐洲聯盟|歐洲聯盟]]就落實雙方自由貿易協議的談判工作，2016年[[比利時|比利時]][[瓦隆|瓦隆]][[瓦隆議會|地區議會]]否決該項協議後她親赴當地游說議員改變初衷<ref name="明報161020">{{cite news |url=http://www.mingpaocanada.com/Tor/htm/News/20161020/tde1_r.htm |title=方慧蘭晤比利時地方領袖 盼挽救加歐自由貿易協議 |publisher=《[[明報|明報]]》加東版 |date=2016-10-20 |accessdate=2017-03-17 |archive-date=2017-03-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170318085444/http://www.mingpaocanada.com/Tor/htm/News/20161020/tde1_r.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。加歐雙方終在2016年10月30日簽定自由貿易協議；在[[美國總統|美國總統]]候選人[[唐納·川普|川普]]鼓吹貿易保護主義以及在[[美墨邊界|美墨邊界]]興建圍牆的背景下，方慧蘭表示這項協議顯示如何在國際關係中「興建橋樑而非圍牆」<ref name="FP">{{cite news |url=http://business.financialpost.com/news/economy/chrystia-freeland-urges-building-bridges-not-walls-to-trade-following-canada-eu-agreement |title=Chrystia Freeland urges 'building bridges, not walls' to trade following Canada-EU agreement |first=Gordon |last=Isfeld |date=2016-10-31 |publisher=《Financial Post》 |accessdate=2017-03-17 |archive-date=2016-11-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161101115016/http://business.financialpost.com/news/economy/chrystia-freeland-urges-building-bridges-not-walls-to-trade-following-canada-eu-agreement |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

====外交部長====
[[File:Secretary_Tillerson_Meets_With_Canadian_Foreign_Minister_Freeland_in_Washington_(32405077340).jpg|thumb]][[雷克斯·蒂勒森|雷克斯·蒂勒森]]會面]]
為了應對川普當選美國總統後的國際政治新形勢，總理杜魯多於2017年1月改組內閣，方慧蘭接替[[斯特凡·迪翁|斯特凡·迪翁]]出任外交部長<ref>{{cite news|first=Robert|last=Fife|title=Trudeau prepares for the Trump era with cabinet shuffle|url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/politics/trudeau-to-shuffle-cabinet-before-trump-inauguration/article33554223/|accessdate=January 10, 2017|work=The Globe and Mail|date=January 9, 2017|archive-date=2017-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170329131533/http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/politics/trudeau-to-shuffle-cabinet-before-trump-inauguration/article33554223/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="CNA170111">{{cite news |url=http://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201701110012-1.aspx |title=加拿大內閣人事大幅異動 外長換人 |publisher=[[中央通訊社|中央通訊社]] |date=2017-01-11 |accessdate=2017-03-17 |archive-date=2018-07-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180707092019/http://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/201701110012-1.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

她於2017年3月與國防部長[[石俊_(政治人物)|石俊]]共同宣布將加拿大軍方為烏克蘭軍隊提供的訓練活動延續至2019年3月，並繼續為該項活動在當地派駐200名加軍<ref name="CBC170306">{{cite news|last1=Brewster|first1=Murray|title=Canada extending military mission in Ukraine to 2019|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/canada-ukraine-military-mission-1.4011870|accessdate=2017-03-17|work=加拿大廣播公司|date=2017-03-06|archive-date=2017-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170309013215/http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/canada-ukraine-military-mission-1.4011870|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[File:Canada_and_Ukraine_meeting_in_Copenhagen_-_2018_(MUS7614).jpg|thumb]]會面（攝於2018年6月）]]
方慧蘭於2019月1月親自到多倫多機場迎接，因報稱受家人虐待而獲庇護的[[沙烏地阿拉伯|沙烏地阿拉伯]]女子{{le|奎農|Rahaf Mohammed}}，並稱她為「非常勇敢的新加拿大人」<ref>{{cite news |url=https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/奎農獲庇護飛抵加拿大-方慧蘭形容勇敢新加拿大人-021400688.html |title=奎農獲庇護飛抵加拿大 方慧蘭形容勇敢新加拿大人 |publisher=《[[星島日報|星島日報]]》（由雅虎新聞刊載） |date=2019-01-11 |accessdate=2019-11-21 |archive-date=2019-06-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190610104834/https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/news/%E5%A5%8E%E8%BE%B2%E7%8D%B2%E5%BA%87%E8%AD%B7%E9%A3%9B%E6%8A%B5%E5%8A%A0%E6%8B%BF%E5%A4%A7-%E6%96%B9%E6%85%A7%E8%98%AD%E5%BD%A2%E5%AE%B9%E5%8B%87%E6%95%A2%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A0%E6%8B%BF%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%BA-021400688.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2019年4月18日，方慧蘭被[[富比世|富比世]]雜誌週年列表中列為第37名優秀領袖，她被指「協商能力強」，以致達成加拿大—歐盟，以及[[美國－墨西哥－加拿大協議|美墨加貿易協議]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://fortune.com/worlds-greatest-leaders/2019/chrystia-freeland|title=Chrystia Freeland|website=Fortune|access-date=November 21, 2019|archive-date=2019-07-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190720172630/https://fortune.com/worlds-greatest-leaders/2019/chrystia-freeland|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==== 副揆 ====
她於[[2019年加拿大聯邦大選|2019年聯邦大選]]在大學－玫瑰谷選區連任下議員。聯邦自由黨在能源和環境等議題上與[[亞伯達省|亞伯達省]]與[[薩克其萬省|薩克其萬省]]的政治分歧日益嚴重，導致自由黨在該屆大選於該兩省全軍覆沒。自由黨雖贏取足夠議席籌組少數政府，但缺乏來自該兩省的議員出任內閣要職。有見及此，總理杜魯多於選後擢升方慧蘭為[[加拿大副總理|加拿大副總理]]兼跨政府事務部長，冀望她在亞伯達省出生的背景有助應對[[加拿大西部|西部]]疏離局面<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.singtao.ca/3936073/2019-11-21/post-%e6%9d%9c%e9%ad%af%e5%a4%9a%e6%96%b0%e5%85%a7%e9%96%a3%e4%ba%ae%e7%9b%b8-%e6%96%b9%e6%85%a7%e8%98%ad%e6%93%a2%e5%8d%87%e5%89%af%e7%b8%bd%e7%90%86/ |title=杜魯多新內閣亮相 方慧蘭擢升副總理 |publisher=《[[星島日報|星島日報]]》加東版 |date=2019-11-21 |accessdate=2019-11-21 }}</ref>。

財長莫奈（{{lang|en|Bill Morneau}}）於2020年8月辭職後，方慧蘭獲杜魯多委派出任該職，成為該國首位女財長，並保留副總理之位；跨政府事務部長職務則由勒布朗（{{lang|fr|Dominic LeBlanc}}）接任<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.singtao.ca/4434464/2020-08-19/post-%e6%96%b9%e6%85%a7%e8%98%ad%e6%89%93%e7%a0%b4%e5%a4%a9%e8%8a%b1%e6%9d%bf-%e6%88%90%e5%8a%a0%e5%9c%8b%e9%a6%96%e4%bd%8d%e5%a5%b3%e8%b2%a1%e9%95%b7/ |title=方慧蘭破「天花板」 成加國首位女財長 |publisher=《[[星島日報|星島日報]]》加東版 |date=2020-08-19 |accessdate=2020-08-25 }}</ref>。

